    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's been kept in a garage and pampered since day one. You won't find a single scratch or a speck of dust on this beauty. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh new-car smell! Come take a look, I promise you're going to fall in love with it!",
