    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the high-revving S54 power plant with precision-timed VANOS and individual throttle bodies. The chassis is structurally optimized with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Mated to a tactile 6-speed Getrag gearbox, the drivetrain exhibits zero lash, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque vectoring. With a pristine service history and factory-spec compression across all cylinders, this vehicle offers an uncompromised analog driving experience in concours condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
