      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, meticulously maintained and kept in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features the original factory deep-gloss finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in 'time-capsule' condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, it is flawless, boasting a complete, documented service history from authorized dealerships with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time. It drives as tight and responsive as the day it rolled off the lot. Complete with both original keys, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title in hand. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a perfect example of this model.",
