    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2001 BMW M3 (E46) Coupe featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is mechanically superlative, boasting a precision Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The S54\u2019s characteristic individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, and the engine remains in peak operating condition following a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural longevity. The chassis retains its original geometry with OEM dampers and bushings, providing the tactile, communicative steering for which the E46 is renowned. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the exterior and interior show zero signs of typical wear, with no pixel degradation or bolster fatigue. A turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
